Question.Subject: What is wrong with FORMSPRING ? ! ANSWER ASAP?
Question.Content: I tried loging into my formspring but this mdb2 error: unknown error keep coming up...when I finally got into my account and tried to reconfigure it back to my facebook, the message came up again ! can somebody please help me and tell me how do i get rid of this thng and what it is...
Question.ChosenAnswer: That seems to happen on Formspring a lot. You can't really do anything about it except to wait a while and try again. It will probably go away after a while.
